synopsis:      GLFW-b demo
description:
  This is a demonstration of GLFW-b
  (<http://hackage.haskell.org/package/GLFW-b>) allowing the user to interact
  with colorful spinning gears using cursor keys, mouse, scroll wheel, and
  joystick.
